            <p>Our team is dedicated to delivering high-quality workmanship, honest pricing, and exceptional customer service on every job, big or small.</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="display:inline-block; margin-top:20px;">Contact Us Today</a>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800" alt="Roofing and Insulation Services">
        </div>
